      <title>美联储杰斐逊：稳定利率有助于抑制通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/fed-s-jefferson-steady-rate-to-help-push-down-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储副主席菲利普·杰斐逊表示，“我的基线前景仍然是通胀将进一步下降，政策利率稳定在当前水平”，但他警告说，持续的价格压力将导致借贷成本在更长时间内保持在高位。华盛顿特区（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/fed-s-jefferson-steady-rate-to-help-push-down-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:52:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Apollo 的 Slok 警告 2022 年市场环境可能会回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/apollo-s-slok-warns-2022-market-environment-might-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Apollo Global Management首席经济学家Torsten Slok表示，将通胀率降至2%可能需要更长的时间，但美联储加息的可能性相对较低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/apollo-s-slok-warns-2022-market-environment-might-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:46:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰推出 30 亿欧元紧缩计划以遏制债务增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/finland-unveils-3-billion-austerity-package-to-halt-debt-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰政府同意追加 30 亿欧元（32 亿美元）的紧缩措施，旨在平衡北欧国家不断恶化的公共财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/finland-unveils-3-billion-austerity-package-to-halt-debt-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:43:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
