      <title>贝莱德的李伟表示，美联储仍希望降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/fed-still-wants-to-cut-rates-blackrock-s-wei-li-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球首席投资策略师李伟在彭博电视台表示，美联储仍希望降息，盈利意外上涨的门槛已经提高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/fed-still-wants-to-cut-rates-blackrock-s-wei-li-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 12:45:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管受到黑客攻击，联合健康集团的利润仍超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/unitedhealth-beats-profit-estimates-despite-hack-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合健康集团公司 (UnitedHealth Group Inc.) 超出华尔街的利润预期并确认了今年的前景，尽管其子公司遭受的网络攻击给医疗保健行业带来了巨大的损失，但该公司的股价还是上涨了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/unitedhealth-beats-profit-estimates-despite-hack-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 投资者支持首席执行官 3900 万美元的薪酬方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stellantis-ceo-s-39-million-pay-package-is-criticized-by-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stellantis NV 股东为卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 扫清了道路，使其成为传统汽车制造商中薪酬最高的首席执行官，这家吉普车制造商在电动汽车转型中追求大幅裁员和严格的节约目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stellantis-ceo-s-39-million-pay-package-is-criticized-by-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
